PROFESSOR: Gravity wins, right?

01:20:44.860 --> 01:20:45.720
And why?

01:20:45.720 --> 01:20:47.630
Intuitively, why does this work?

01:20:47.630 --> 01:20:50.139
AUDIENCE: [MURMURING]

01:20:50.139 --> 01:20:51.930
PROFESSOR: I am neglecting
